{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/103300", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/103300/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/103300/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/103300/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/103300", "id": 1416446428, "node_id": "I_kwDOAAsO6M5UbUHc", "number": 103300, "title": "Conditionally derived traits using `cfg_attr` are not documented as being behind a feature flag.", "user": {"login": "cobward", "id": 93085583, "node_id": "U_kgDOBYxfjw", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/93085583?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/cobward", "html_url": "https://github.com/cobward", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cobward/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cobward/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cobward/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cobward/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cobward/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cobward/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cobward/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cobward/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cobward/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 203738, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwyMDM3Mzg=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/T-rustdoc", "name": "T-rustdoc", "color": "bfd4f2", "default": false, "description": "Relevant to the rustdoc team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue."}], "state": "open", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 2, "created_at": "2022-10-20T11:26:09Z", "updated_at": "2023-02-01T18:10:00Z", "closed_at": null, "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "When conditionally deriving a trait using `cfg_attr`, the `doc_cfg` feature gate is not documented. A minimal example can be found [here](https://github.com/cobward/doc_cfg_attr_issue), but is summarised below:\r\n\r\n## Example:\r\n```rust\r\n #![feature(doc_auto_cfg)]\r\n #[cfg_attr(feature = \"debug\", derive(Debug))]\r\n pub struct Test();\r\n```\r\n### Generates:\r\n![generated](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/93085583/196935828-ab68f9fe-0075-426e-ad15-9d0d81fea049.png)\r\n\r\n### Expectation:\r\n![expected](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/93085583/196935838-cb4953b2-a5b8-477c-827e-aa964e2e3779.png)\r\n", "closed_by": null, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/103300/reactions", "total_count": 1, "+1": 1, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/103300/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}